<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User - Smart Door Lock System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav_container">
            <a href="/home"><p>Smart Door Lock System</p></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="welcoming_container">
        <p>WELCOME BACK <%= name %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="main-product-content">
        <div class="product-content">
            <h2>LOCK STATUS</h2>
            <div class="stateOfLock stateOpen">
                <div class="stateOfLockText textOpen"></div>
            </div>

            <h2>AUTO LOCK?</h2>
            <button class="open-block-btn" id="toggle-lock">YES</button>

            <h2>LOCK PASSWORD REGISTER</h2>
            <div id="lock-pass">
                <form action="/register-lock-password" method="POST">
                    <input type="hidden" name="lockId" value="your-lock-id-here">
                    <input type="password" name="lockPassword" placeholder="Enter Lock Password" required>
                    <button type="submit">Register</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tutorial">
            <h2>ACCESS HISTORY</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Aperiam veritatis dolorum, voluptates ad provident incidunt blanditiis recusandae? Possimus magnam, quisquam voluptas laboriosam accusantium repellendus, esse enim labore consequuntur asperiores suscipit.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/main.js"></script>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('beforeunload', function (e) {
            // Send a request to the server to handle logout
            navigator.sendBeacon('/logout');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
